//		output) 곱하기, x=?
		
//		Declare variable a,b
//		in case of *, if x is integer and x meet the condition above
//		print "곱하기 x"
//		in case of +, if x is integer and x meet the condition above
//		print "더하기 x"
//		in case of -, if x is integer and x meet the condition above
//		print 
//		Otherwise, print "Doesn't exit"
